latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hey guys, excited to launch @dreamdeal.me, the first of its kind platform to help people’s ideas take flight. We will provide micro grants & mentorship to inspire & help people move one step ahead on their entrepreneurial journey 🦋

All you have to do is post a 30-second reel with your X, Y & Z - explained on @dreamdeal.me 

10 of the best ideas will be selected, out of which -

✅ The number 1 pitch will receive a grant of Rs.1 lac

✅ 2 more pitches will receive Rs. 75 k each

✅ The remaining 7 will receive a group mentorship session

 🚀 Winners will be selected based on 1) novelty & potential impact of the idea, 2) creativity & 3) post likes & engagement

🚀 All the challenge rules & selection criteria are posted on @dreamdeal.me

So, what you waiting for? Put on your thinking hat, click-through to @dreamdeal.me, follow the handle, read the rules and make your reel. That simple 😅

Here’s a kicker 🥾to get you off your butt. The 1st 5 reels get 5 k 💰each… seriously (as long as u stick to the rules) 🙄
 
Pls share this post with all the young & aspiring entrepreneurs you know 📣 Good luck 🍀

68% of women graduates in India are not in the work-force today... Let that sink in! Why are India’s women leaving the work-force at such an astonishing rate? 😢

Closing the gender gap can add $50b-$100b💪 to India’s GDP every year and accelerate our journey towards becoming a leading power. 

I am super excited to partner with @bhumipednekar to launch Shaadi.org, a social initiative from @shaadi.com, and dedicate ourselves towards helping drive this change. Because it’s not just the right thing to do, it’s also the smart thing👩‍🎓 to do … for our economy & our nation.

Yeh hamara kartavya hi nahin, yeh hamara karam bhi hai. #AnEqualNation is a more powerful nation. #Jaihind 🇮🇳 

#WomensDay #TogetherWithWomen #IndiaRising #BreakTheBias

Ever considered what went behind a revolution that created 7 Million success stories* ? 💞

Why @shaadi.com started out and how it became a success? 🥂 

We thought it was a story that needed to be told & wondered whether we could go back in time and recreate the magical moments 🪄🦄

It was risky but we convinced our founder @anupammittal.me to become 20 yrs younger (seriously 🫣) and act out the incredible startup journey of @Shaadi.com, a story that celebrates the undying spirit of #entrepreneurship 🧗‍♂️ #togetherness 👫 & never giving up 💪

Show some love ❤️ if you like the effort or tell us what we could have done better 👇
